caption.title: Rates of infection, dissemination efficiency and transmission efficiency for CHIKV, DENV and ZIKV in AR wP and AR wP-M Ae. Albopictus.
caption.p: IR = Infection rate; DE = Dissemination rate; TE = transmission rate; A: the differences between Ae. albopictus lines are significant with respect to all of the three parameters and at both time intervals (7, 14 dpi) post the infection (Fisher exact test, P < 0.05); B: AR wP and AR wP-M significantly differed with regard to IR and DE at 14 dpi (Fisher exact test, P < 0.05); C: AR wP and AR wP-M did not significantly differ with regard to any of the evaluated parameters.
